OL,4,CNorthumberland Longridge Towers School
OL,5,Cstrip club teacher banned
OL,6, An IT teacher who threatened pupils and
OL,7, took some to a strip club while he was
OL,8, drunk during a school trip has been
OL,9, banned from teaching for three years.
OL,11,FRichard Glenn's behaviour was so
OL,12,F"unacceptable" he was sent home early
OL,13,Fduring Longridge Towers School's trip
OL,14,Fto Costa Rica in July 2019, the
OL,15,FTeaching Regulation Agency heard.
OL,17,FMr Glenn, 55, admitted gross misconduct
OL,18,Fand was dismissed in August 2019.
OL,20,FThe Northumberland private school costs
OL,21,Fup to #4,850 a term for day pupils.
